Foliate is a simple and modern GTK eBook viewer, built with gjs and Epub.js.
Features:
- View .epub, .mobi, .azw, and .azw3 files in two-page view or scrolled view
- Customize font, line-spacing, margins, and brightness
- Light, sepia, dark, and invert mode, or add your own custom themes
- Reading progress slider with chapter marks
- Bookmarks and annotations
- Find in book
- Quick dictionary lookup with Wiktionary and `dictd`, or translate text with Google Translate
- Touchpad gestures use two-finger swipe to turn the page
- Basic text-to-speech support with eSpeak NG ad Festival
